story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0100_10:
This is a jam session featurin’ Team Yell and Team
Skull! Let’s make some noise!
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0200_10:
Yeah, I can get behind that! I’mma make y’all hear
the sound of DESTRUCTION!
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0300_10:
I can already hear the sound of destruction! But
the only sound Team Rocket will make is a
whimper of defeat!
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0400_10: My cheers will really get you goin’, Team Skull!
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0500_10: Yo, big sis Marnie! Can I be your fan?
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0600_10:
C’mon, Plumeria! Show ’em how cool you are and
finish ’em off!
story_final_02_05000/2401_1201_0700_10: It’s not so bad, getting cheered on like this...
